OL,3,CMobile phones having poor impact on
OL,4,Cpupil behaviour, survey says
OL,6,FSome 71% of secondary school teachers
OL,7,Fsay mobile phones are having a poor
OL,8,Fimpact on pupil behaviour, according
OL,9,Fto a survey.
OL,11,FIn its annual survey, the Scottish
OL,12,FSecondary Teachers Association (SSTA)
OL,13,Feducation committee found that its
OL,14,Fmembers held a number of concerns
OL,15,Fregarding mobile phones in the
OL,16,Fclassroom.
OL,18,FThe survey took place in February
OL,19,F2024, with 1,451 members responding.
