OL,3,CMobile phones having poor impact on
OL,4,Cpupil behaviour, survey says
OL,6,FMeanwhile, 90% of respondents reported
OL,7,Fpupils having detachment problems,
OL,8,Fwith the same percentage stating they
OL,9,Fwere concerned that pupils had been
OL,10,Ftexting during lessons.
OL,12,FWhile 80% reported pupils taking
OL,13,Fphotos on their phones during class,
OL,14,Fand 60% said they were worried about
OL,15,Fsocial media bullying, with phones in
OL,16,Fthe classroom being a factor.
