OL,3,CMobile phones having poor impact on
OL,4,Cpupil behaviour, survey says
OL,6,FRespondents also said pupils had
OL,7,Fanswered calls during lessons, viewed
OL,8,Finappropriate content, and had
OL,9,Fbroadcasted live recordings of lessons
OL,10,Fonline.
OL,12,FIn total, almost all of the
OL,13,Frespondents told the survey their
OL,14,Fclasses had been interrupted due to
OL,15,Fmobile phones.
OL,17,FSeamus Searson, SSTA general secretary
OL,18,Fsaid: "92% of members said their
OL,19,Flessons were being interrupted by
OL,20,Fasking pupils to put away their mobile
OL,21,Fphones.
