OL,4,Cpupil behaviour, survey says
OL,6,FTwo thirds (67%) said phones were to
OL,7,Fbe placed on their teacher's desk if
OL,8,Fthey were caught using them in lessons.
OL,10,FOther teachers have told to put their
OL,11,Fphones on silent, with some asking
OL,12,Fthem to place their phones into a box
OL,13,For similar at the start of lessons.
OL,15,FTeachers would also issue detentions,
OL,16,Fdemerits, and messages to the parents
OL,17,Fof schoolkids caught using phones in
OL,18,Fclass.
