OL,6,FThey would also confiscate phones, but
OL,7,Fsaid this led to confrontation from
OL,8,Fpupils due to the possibility of theft.
OL,10,FJames Cowans, SSTA education convenor
OL,11,Fsaid: "62% of members saw the benefits
OL,12,Fof using mobile phones in helping with
OL,13,Flessons.
OL,15,F"In many cases this was due to the
OL,16,Flack of access to other mobile devices
OL,17,For poor connectivity within the school.
