OL,6,FIndependent boarding school
OL,7,FGordonstoun has limited the use of
OL,8,Fmobile phones since 2017, and since
OL,9,F2023, has informed pupils to leave
OL,10,Ftheir phones in boarding houses
OL,11,Fthroughout the day and hand them to
OL,12,Fstaff overnight.
OL,14,FSixth year pupils may keep their
OL,15,Fphones, but must be switched off
OL,16,Fduring the school day.
