OL,9,Fcurb the negative impact of mobiles in
OL,10,Fclass.
OL,12,FShe said: "It seems we have now
OL,13,Freached a tipping point where the
OL,14,Fdevices are doing more harm than good
OL,15,Fto the extent it's preventing teachers
OL,16,Ffrom doing their jobs properly.
